title: Protests as Catalonia threatens declaration of independence from Spain
description:
A regional leader in Spain wants to break away and form a new country, but he is under growing pressure not to do that. Huge rallies Sunday condemned the government of Catalonia's vow to declare independence after a disputed referendum. Seth Doane reports from Barcelona.
